
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "GACContent";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutPublic.cshtml";
}

<section class="breadcrumbs">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <h2><b>Content Classification for Appeal </b></h2>
            <ol>
                <li><a href=@Url.Action("Index","Home",new {Area=""})>Home</a></li>
                <li>GAC </li>
                <li>Content Classification </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="inner-page">
    <div class="container">
        <p>Four GACs are proposed as following for dealing with the Appeals as per content classification:</p>
        <p style="font-weight: 700">GAC 1: Women & Child Safety </p>
        <p style="margin-top: -20px;">(Sexual Content)</p>
        <p style="font-weight: 700">GAC 2: Matters of State & Criminal Justice </p>
        <p style="margin-top: -20px;">(Content hampering National Integrity/ Impersonation or Discrimination)</p>
        <p style="font-weight: 700">GAC 3: Responsible Use of Information</p>
        <p style="margin-top: -20px;">(Content spreading misinformation or disinformation)</p>
        <p style="font-weight: 700">GAC 4: Residual Cases & Other Due Diligence by Intermediaries</p>
        <p style="margin-top: -20px;">(Computer Virus/ Cases requiring MeitY intervention)</p>

        <table class="table table-striped-columns" style="    border: 1px solid #ccc;">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col">Content Classification for Appeal</th>
                    <th scope="col">GAC Subject Matter </th>

                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p style="font-weight: 700">Sexual Content</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Exposes Private Area</li>
                            <li>Shows individual in full or partial nudity </li>
                            <li>Shows person in any sexual act or conduct</li>
                            <li>Impersonation in an electronic form</li>
                            <li>Artificially morphed images of the individual</li>
                            <li>Invasive of another’s bodily privacy</li>
                        </ul>
                        <span style="font-weight: 700">Harmful to children</span> (Except Child Sexual Abuse/Exploitation Material)
                    </td>
                    <td><span style="font-weight: 700">GAC 1: </span>Women & Child Safety</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p style="font-weight: 700">Content hampering National Integrity </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Promoting enmity between different groups on the grounds of religion or caste with the intent to incite violence</li>
                            <li>Threatens the unity, integrity, defence, security or sovereignty of India</li>
                            <li>Threatens friendly relations with foreign states</li>
                            <li>Threatens public order</li>
                            <li>Causes incitement to the commission of any cognisable offence</li>
                            <li>Prevents investigation of any offence</li>
                            <li>Is insulting other nation</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="font-weight: 700">Impersonation or Discrimination</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Impersonates another person</li>
                            <li>Insulting harassing on the basis of gender Racially or ethnically objectionable</li>
                        </ul>
                    </td>
                    <td><span style="font-weight: 700">GAC 2: </span>Matters of State & Criminal Justice</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p style="font-weight: 700">Content spreading misinformation or disinformation </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Deceives or misleads the addressee about the origin of the message</li>
                            <li>Knowingly and intentionally communicates any misinformation or information which is patently false and untrue or misleading in nature</li>
                        </ul>

                    </td>
                    <td><span style="font-weight: 700">GAC 3:</span> Responsible Use of Information</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p style="font-weight: 700">Computer Virus/Cases requiring MeitY intervention</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Software virus or any other computer code, file or program designed to interrupt, destroy or limit the functionality of any computer resource</li>
                            <li>Appeals related to cases where MeitY intervention is required and residual cases</li>
                        </ul>

                    </td>
                    <td><span style="font-weight: 700">GAC 4:</span> Residual cases & other Due Diligence by Intermediaries</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</section>

